---
const linkedInUrl =
  import.meta.env.PUBLIC_LINKEDIN_URL?.trim() ||
  "https://www.linkedin.com/in/cale-clarke-4636a12b/";
---

<section id="about" class="about-root" aria-labelledby="about-heading">
  <h2 id="about-heading" class="section-title">About me</h2>
  <div class="about-prose">
    <p>
      I’m <strong>Cale Clarke</strong> — Catholic broadcaster, podcaster, speaker, and writer. I explain and defend the Faith through Scripture. I founded <strong>The Faith Explained Institute</strong>.
    </p>
    <p>
      I studied at St. Mary’s University and Tyndale Seminary, with postgraduate work alongside Dr. Craig A. Evans. I’m grateful for my years with Relevant Radio; today my focus is <em>The Cale Clarke Show</em>, speaking, pilgrimages, and this community. I live near Toronto with my wife, Patricia, and our daughter, Michaela.
    </p>
    <p class="about-linkedin">
      <a href={linkedInUrl} rel="noopener noreferrer" target="_blank">
        Venues, media, and experience — LinkedIn →
      </a>
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .about-root {
    scroll-margin-top: 80px;
    padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .section-title {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: clamp(1.5rem, 2.5vw, 2rem);
    font-weight: 600;
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-md);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .about-prose p {
    margin: 0 0 var(--space-sm);
    color: var(--color-ink-muted);
    max-width: var(--prose-width);
    font-size: 1.0625rem;
    line-height: 1.75;
  }

  .about-prose strong {
    color: var(--color-ink);
    font-weight: 600;
  }

  .about-linkedin {
    margin-top: var(--space-md) !important;
  }

  .about-linkedin a {
    font-weight: 600;
  }
</style>
